       <h1 class ="new" style="color: black; line-height:1.6; text-align:left; font-weight: normal;">Welcome to the Fraction Corral! There are 6 levels of difficulty for this game, ranging from one to 6 stars. For each level you will have to answer 3 sets of 5 questions. You will have 45 seconds to answer each question set. You first select one of the five fractions displayed at the top of the screen, then select its equivalent fraction from the fraction corral. 20 points are awarded for each correct comparison, a total of 300 points are possible over the 3 sets of questions. In order to pass a level, you have to get above 240 or more points after the 15 questions. See if you can pass them all, good luck!!
